{"tid":1218390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以屌醒班離地港豬","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:56:30.000Z","uid":58703,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97a6c183fa1364e31a0494e84bcfc047f7d81c72","tid":1218390,"uid":58703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:40:04.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打話不如遊行唱 Do You Hear The People Sing<br />\n諗起今日見到一個港女IG Story：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kr5wrVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKr5wrVy.jpg&h=9aef508d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有無人見到依啲 Post 會好撚火滾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依幾日香港發生左咁多事<br />\n無論係和理非定係熱血既年青人<br />\n大家都有賣心賣力為香港人發聲<br />\n然後有啲港豬又搞埋啲咩拍片、錄音唱歌<br />\n根本無任何用．亦都無noise<br />\n<br />\n咩叫「唔覺我地幾有能力做到d 咩」？<br />\n你當依幾日出黎遊行既人死㗎？<br />\n你當依幾日出黎唱聖詩既基督徒死㗎？<br />\n你當依幾日幫手提供補給既巴絲死㗎？<br />\n<br />\n你當我主觀地覺得依啲行為<span style=\"font-size: large;\">呃like</span> 啦<br />\n你可能覺得：人地都係用其他方法表達下自己聲音<br />\n<br />\n佢下一個story<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9MTNKKw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9MTNKKw.jpg&h=8dd45467&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我一見到真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哇</span>左一聲<br />\n上一個story 仲問有無人有興趣一齊<span style=\"color: red;\">背住</span>或者<span style=\"color: red;\">蒙面唱歌</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">下一個story 就貼撚曬你地班友出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n啲名我幫你遮撚曬啦傻閪<br />\n真係不怕神一樣的對手<br />\n只怕豬一樣的隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想講一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">自己香港自己救<br />\n經歷過 6.9/ 6.12 之後<br />\n我更加相信只要大家齊心<br />\n無論係不合作運動、遊行、唱聖詩定提供後援<br />\n我地都可以以自己既力量影響香港！<br />\n各位巴絲繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4ea099121b11866786a439dce3a36d9443cd65a5","tid":1218390,"uid":58703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8b04e602b57aee44f140d846fc68b3900efdc716","tid":1218390,"uid":58703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"291547be33d5dd893de2c8b59dd5bf2e19feb4fb","tid":1218390,"uid":58703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"31f82800a18d1eb3101ba6ad23957f30296fbeff","tid":1218390,"uid":258656,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"呢個時候仲搞分化？邊個係港豬唔洗講都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd94070f866dc4b8c60af87db485fe255718992","tid":1218390,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}